## Warehouse Access Roles

{%- if account_strategy == 'Single Account' %}
{%- set prefix = data_product_domain | upper ~ '_' ~ data_product_name | upper ~ '_' ~ data_product_environment | upper %}
{%- elif account_strategy == 'Multi-Account (Environment-based)' %}
{%- set prefix = data_product_domain | upper ~ '_' ~ data_product_name | upper %}
{%- elif account_strategy == 'Multi-Account (Domain-based)' %}
{%- set prefix = data_product_name | upper ~ '_' ~ data_product_environment | upper %}
{%- elif account_strategy == 'Multi-Account (Domain + Environment)' %}
{%- set prefix = data_product_name | upper %}
{%- endif %}

### Access Roles to Create

| Warehouse | Access Role | Privileges |
|-----------|-------------|------------|
{%- for wh in warehouse_configuration %}
| `{{ prefix }}_WH_{{ wh.name | upper }}` | `{{ prefix }}_WH_U_{{ wh.name | upper }}` | USAGE, MONITOR, OPERATE |
{%- endfor %}

### Role Properties

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| **Owner** | `{{ prefix }}_RBAC` |
| **Can Grant** | Any role via RBAC |

### Access Pattern

```
User → Account Role → Warehouse Access Role → Warehouse
                            ↓
                     USAGE, MONITOR, OPERATE
```

### Recommended Assignments

| Warehouse Type | Typical Users |
|----------------|---------------|
| ETL/Transform | Data Engineers, Service Accounts |
| Analytics | Data Analysts, BI Tools |
| Interactive | Ad-hoc query users |
| Production | Application service accounts |
